#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_banner
msgid ""
"<br/>Enjoy breathtaking views of nature. Relax and embrace your dreams.<br/"
"><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/> Njut av en hisnande utsikt över naturen. Koppla av och omfamna dina "
"drömmar.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_company_team
msgid ""
"Aline designs bespoke travel itineraries, collaborating with a global "
"network of experts to deliver unique experiences tailored to each client's "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Aline utformar skräddarsydda resplaner och samarbetar med ett globalt "
"nätverk av experter för att leverera unika upplevelser anpassade till varje "
"kunds behov."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_banner
msgid ""
"An unforgettable experience! Every destination was stunning, and the service "
"was exceptional."
msgstr ""
"En oförglömlig upplevelse! Varje destination var fantastisk och servicen var "
"enastående."

